The paper focuses on query rewriting for sponsored search, which is a problem in information retrieval (IR) and search engines. Therefore, cs.IR is the most likely sub-category. The paper also uses link analysis and graph algorithms, which are common in social networks and web mining, making cs.SI and cs.DS likely sub-categories as well. The paper also deals with data management and manipulation, which falls under cs.DB. Finally, the paper uses machine learning techniques to improve the query rewriting, which is a topic in cs.LG.
